@7690 = ~Some believe this massive blade to be of drow origin, though others dispute this claim. However, all agree this great sword was fashioned with a single purpose... to rid the world of the illithid. The attacks from the Psion's Blade inflict grievous wounds on illithids, and those who wield it are immune to the mind flayer's psionic attacks. The bewildering gaze of umber hulks, often found serving the illithid, are similarly rendered harmless.

